OL,3,CBen & Jerry's co-founder quits,
OL,4,Caccusing Unilever of stifling social
OL,5,Cactivism
OL,7,FBen & Jerry's co-founder Jerry
OL,8,FGreenfield has quit the company after
OL,9,Falmost half a decade, accusing parent
OL,10,Fcompany Unilever of stifling the
OL,11,Foutspoken ice cream brand.
OL,13,FUnilever acquired Ben & Jerry's in
OL,14,F2000 for $326 million (around #240
OL,15,Fmillion). At the time, Ben & Jerry's
OL,16,Fsaid the partnership would help the
OL,17,Fprogressive ice cream company expand
OL,18,Fits social mission.
