OL,3,CBen & Jerry's co-founder quits,
OL,4,Caccusing Unilever of stifling social
OL,5,Cactivism
OL,7,FBut relations have soured in recent
OL,8,Fyears, after the company decided to
OL,9,Fstop selling ice cream in Israeli
OL,10,Fsettlements in the occupied West Bank
OL,11,Fand contested East Jerusalem.
OL,13,FWhen Unilever planned to sell its
OL,14,FIsraeli business to a local company
OL,15,Fthat would sell Ben & Jerry's
OL,16,Fthroughout Israel and the West Bank
OL,17,Fusing Hebrew and Arabic trademarks,
OL,18,FBen & Jerry's sued. A judge later
OL,19,Fthrew out the request to halt the move.
