OL,3,CBen & Jerry's co-founder quits,
OL,4,Caccusing Unilever of stifling social
OL,5,Cactivism
OL,7,FAnother lawsuit came in November 2024,
OL,8,Fwhen Ben & Jerry's accused Unilever of
OL,9,Fengaging in "inappropriate muzzling"
OL,10,Fby blocking the company from speaking
OL,11,Fout in support of Palestinians.
OL,13,FIn March, Ben & Jerry's said that its
OL,14,FCEO was unlawfully removed by Unilever
OL,15,Fin retaliation for the ice cream
OL,16,Fmaker's social and political activism,
OL,17,Fsaying it violated its merger
OL,18,Fagreement with the parent company.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
