OL,3,CBen & Jerry's co-founder quits,
OL,4,Caccusing Unilever of stifling social
OL,5,Cactivism
OL,7,FCo-founder Ben Cohen published a
OL,8,Fletter written by Greenfield on social
OL,9,Fmedia platform X, along with the
OL,10,Fhashtag _FreeBenAndJerrys.
OL,12,FGreenfield said that leaving the ice
OL,13,Fcream company was "one of the hardest
OL,14,Fand most painful decisions I've ever
OL,15,Fmade", and blamed Unilever for
OL,16,Fsilencing the company's independence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
