OL,3,CBen & Jerry's co-founder quits,
OL,4,Caccusing Unilever of stifling social
OL,5,Cactivism
OL,7,F"For more than 20 years under their
OL,8,Fownership, Ben & Jerry's stood up and
OL,9,Fspoke out in support of peace, justice
OL,10,Fand human rights, not as abstract
OL,11,Fconcepts, but in relation to real
OL,12,Fevents happening in our world," he
OL,13,Fwrote.
OL,15,F"That independence existed in no small
OL,16,Fpart because of the unique merger
OL,17,Fagreement Ben and I negotiated with
OL,18,FUnilever, one that enshrined our
OL,19,Fsocial mission and values in the
OL,20,Fcompany's governance structure in
OL,21,Fperpetuity.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
