OL,3,CBen & Jerry's co-founder quits,
OL,4,Caccusing Unilever of stifling social
OL,5,Cactivism
OL,7,F"It's profoundly disappointing to come
OL,8,Fto the conclusion that that
OL,9,Findependence, the very basis of our
OL,10,Fsale to Unilever, is gone."
OL,12,FHe noted that Unilever's alleged
OL,13,Fstifling of Ben & Jerry's independence
OL,14,Fwas coming "at a time when our
OL,15,Fcountry's current administration is
OL,16,Fattacking civil rights, voting rights,
OL,17,Fthe rights of immigrants, women and
OL,18,Fthe LGBTQ community".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
