OL,3,CBen & Jerry's co-founder quits,
OL,4,Caccusing Unilever of stifling social
OL,5,Cactivism
OL,7,F"Standing up for the values of
OL,8,Fjustice, equity, and our shared
OL,9,Fhumanity has never been more
OL,10,Fimportant, and yet Ben & Jerry's has
OL,11,Fbeen silenced, sidelined for fear of
OL,12,Fupsetting those in power," he added.
OL,14,F"It's easy to stand up and speak out
OL,15,Fwhen there's nothing at risk. The real
OL,16,Ftest of values is when times are
OL,17,Fchallenging and you have something to
OL,18,Flose."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
