OL,3,CBen & Jerry's co-founder quits,
OL,4,Caccusing Unilever of stifling social
OL,5,Cactivism
OL,7,FUnilever, based in London, is spinning
OL,8,Foff its ice cream business, including
OL,9,FBen & Jerry's into a stand-alone
OL,10,Fcompany called The Magnum Ice Cream
OL,11,FCompany.
OL,13,FA spokesperson for Magnum said in a
OL,14,Fstatement on Wednesday that it would
OL,15,Fbe forever grateful to Greenfield for
OL,16,Fhis contributions to Ben & Jerry's and
OL,17,Fthanked him for his service, but was
OL,18,Fnot aligned with his viewpoint.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
