OL,3,CBen & Jerry's co-founder quits,
OL,4,Caccusing Unilever of stifling social
OL,5,Cactivism
OL,7,F"We disagree with his perspective and
OL,8,Fhave sought to engage both co-founders
OL,9,Fin a constructive conversation on how
OL,10,Fto strengthen Ben & Jerry's powerful
OL,11,Fvalues-based position in the world,"
OL,12,Fthe spokesperson said.
OL,14,FMagnum said that it is still committed
OL,15,Fto Ben & Jerry's mission and remains
OL,16,F"focused on carrying forward the
OL,17,Flegacy of peace, love, and ice cream
OL,18,Fof this iconic, much-loved brand."
